- HAVE ANY HERMAPHRODITES?

01:28.689 --> 01:30.724
- I DON'T THINK SO.
- GOOD.

01:30.758 --> 01:32.493
GO FUCK YOURSELF.
- [chuckles]

01:32.526 --> 01:34.195
- ANYBODY HERE WORTH DOING?

01:34.228 --> 01:35.863
- NO, SORRY, BRI.
ALREADY DONE THEM.

01:35.896 --> 01:38.132
- OH, WE WERE UP TO FRIDAY.

01:38.166 --> 01:40.201
- OH, UH, THERE'S FRIDAY
OVER THERE.

01:40.234 --> 01:41.535
THE BOSSY BOTTOM
OVER THERE.

01:41.569 --> 01:43.237
- HE'S A BOTTOM?
- YEAH.

01:43.271 --> 01:44.905
YOU SHOULD HEAR HIM
SING NATURAL WOMAN.

01:44.938 --> 01:46.340
BETTER THAN ARETHA,
I MIGHT ADD.

01:46.374 --> 01:47.741
- YOU'VE GOT TO GAG THEM FIRST,

01:47.775 --> 01:49.877
THEN FUCK 'EM.

01:49.910 --> 01:52.546
YOU STILL HAVE MUCH TO LEARN,
THEODORE.

01:52.580 --> 01:54.282
- OH MY GOD.
WHO'S THAT?

01:54.315 --> 02:02.256
*

02:10.664 --> 02:14.402
- I DON'T KNOW, BUT I BELIEVE
I HAVE SUNDAY FREE.

02:14.435 --> 02:16.370
- COUNT ON STAYING HOME

02:16.404 --> 02:19.207
AND TRIMMING YOUR PUBES.

02:23.277 --> 02:25.413
- I'LL LET HIM
HAVE THIS ONE.

02:25.446 --> 02:28.649
- [chuckles] YEAH.

