AREN'T WE?

27:38.357 --> 27:39.826
- HAPPY NEW HOUSE.
[chuckles]

27:39.859 --> 27:40.927
- THANKS.

27:40.960 --> 27:41.928
YOU MIND
IF I SHOW HER OFF?

27:41.961 --> 27:45.898
- BE MY GUEST.

27:45.932 --> 27:48.801
HEY, EVERYONE, MEET
MY BEAUTIFUL DAUGHTER.

27:48.835 --> 27:51.203
[all exclaiming]

27:51.237 --> 27:53.239
- HEY.
