27:53.272 --> 27:55.374
- HEY, LOOK WHO IT IS.
- SHE'S CUTE.

27:55.407 --> 27:57.209
- I KNOW!

27:57.243 --> 27:59.712
- FIRST I'M GOING TO GIVE HIM
THE FUCKING OF HIS LIFE,

27:59.746 --> 28:01.247
THEN I'M GOING TO GIVE HIM
THE MIND-FUCKING OF HIS LIFE.

28:01.280 --> 28:03.315
I'M GOING TO SAY, "ONCE
I WAS YOUR PITY-FUCK,

28:03.349 --> 28:07.053
