YOU ARROGANT ASSHOLE."

28:07.086 --> 28:08.721
- SPEAKING OF WHICH...

28:08.755 --> 28:10.322
- AREN'T YOU TWO AUNTIES
GOING TO GO

28:10.356 --> 28:14.827
"OOH" AND "AHH"
OVER THE BABY?

28:14.861 --> 28:18.197
I CAUGHT YOUR UNDERPANTS
ON THE NEWS THE OTHER NIGHT.

28:18.230 --> 28:20.199
YOU SAVING YOUR DICK
FOR SWEEPS?

28:20.232 --> 28:23.369
- MY PRODUCER HAPPENED TO THINK
IT WAS A TERRIFIC SEGMENT.

28:23.402 --> 28:25.104
YEAH, HE SAID
IT WAS ABOUT TIME

28:25.137 --> 28:28.074
WE SAW GAY PEOPLE AS FULL,
SEXUALISED HUMAN BEINGS,

28:28.107 --> 28:32.979
NOT JUST STEREOTYPIC
EUNUCHS AND CLOWNS.

28:33.012 --> 28:36.048
NOW IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME.

28:43.122 --> 28:45.157
- OUR DAUGHTER'S A HIT.
- HMM.

28:45.191 --> 28:48.360
I'D SAY SO.

28:48.394 --> 28:49.962
- GLAD YOU CAME.

28:49.996 --> 28:51.831
- MM.

28:51.864 --> 28:55.835
IF FOR NO OTHER REASON,
I'M STARVING.

28:55.868 --> 28:59.972
- IT MAKES ME THINK
OF OUR HOUSEWARMING.

29:00.006 --> 29:02.374
- IF ANYONE NEEDS PROOF
THAT TOILETS

29:02.408 --> 29:04.143
ARE CONTROLLED
BY COSMIC FORCES...

29:04.176 --> 29:05.544
- WHY ELSE WOULD
THEY BREAK DOWN

29:05.577 --> 29:07.313
TEN MINUTES BEFORE
THE GUESTS SHOWED UP?

29:07.346 --> 29:09.315
- A HUNDRED DYKES PEEING
IN THE BACKYARD.

29:09.348 --> 29:12.985
- THE BUSHES IN THE BUSHES.

29:13.019 --> 29:18.324
[both giggling]

29:18.357 --> 29:19.859
[clinking]

29:19.892 --> 29:21.027
- EVERYBODY.

29:21.060 --> 29:23.262
- CAN WE HAVE
YOUR ATTENTION?

29:23.295 --> 29:26.999
WE'D JUST LIKE TO
WELCOME ALL OF YOU

29:27.033 --> 29:28.400
TO OUR NEW HOME.

29:28.434 --> 29:30.469
- BEAUTIFUL NEW HOME.

29:30.502 --> 29:32.071
- AND WE LOOK FORWARD
TO SHARING

29:32.104 --> 29:35.074
MANY HAPPY FAMILY OCCASIONS
HERE TOGETHER.

29:35.107 --> 29:37.276
[cheers and applause]

29:37.309 --> 29:39.879
- HAPPY FAMILY OCCASIONS.

29:39.912 --> 29:44.016
- WE ALSO HAVE ANOTHER REASON
TO CELEBRATE TONIGHT.

29:44.050 --> 29:47.887
RAGE AND J.T.
ARE GETTING MARRIED.

29:47.920 --> 29:50.356
- IT'S ABOUT TIME THOSE
TWO SUPERHEROES SETTLED DOWN!

29:50.389 --> 29:53.025
- WHEN DO THEY START RAISING
A SUPER FAMILY?

29:53.059 --> 29:54.093
- THAT'S NEXT.

29:54.126 --> 29:55.427
- GOT A COPY FOR EVERYONE.

29:55.461 --> 29:58.965
OUR LITTLE HOUSEWARMING
GIFT TO YOU.

29:58.998 --> 30:01.100
HERE YOU GO, BRIAN.

30:01.133 --> 30:04.070
[overlapping chatter]

30:06.138 --> 30:07.806
HERE YOU ARE.
- YOU LIKE IT?

30:10.276 --> 30:12.044
- REMINDS ME OF
THIS NORMAN ROCKWELL

30:12.078 --> 30:14.313
I SAW IN THE DOCTOR'S OFFICE
WHEN I WAS A KID.

30:14.346 --> 30:18.050
A LITTLE GIRL AND BOY DRESSED
AS A BRIDE AND GROOM

30:18.084 --> 30:21.854
AND THEIR ADORABLE PUPPY
TUGGING ON THE BRIDAL GOWN.

30:21.888 --> 30:23.355
JUST THEN THE NURSE
CAME IN AND STABBED ME

30:23.389 --> 30:25.124
IN THE FINGER FOR BLOOD.

30:25.157 --> 30:27.927
- AND YOU'VE HAD AN AVERSION
TO MARRIAGE EVER SINCE?

30:27.960 --> 30:31.197
WELL, I HAPPEN TO THINK
IT'S A DAMN GOOD STORY.

30:31.230 --> 30:33.365
JUST BECAUSE IT DOESN'T AGREE
WITH YOUR ANTI-FAMILY VALUES

30:33.399 --> 30:37.069
IS NO REASON TO DUMP ON IT.

30:37.103 --> 30:39.038
- OKAY.

30:47.279 --> 30:49.148
- LET'S GET
THE WHOLE FAMILY.

30:49.181 --> 30:50.516
HOW DO YOU WORK
THIS THING?

30:50.549 --> 30:52.351
- GOOD IDEA.
I'LL--I'LL GET J.R.

30:52.384 --> 30:54.853
YOU GET HUNTER.
- OKAY.

30:57.656 --> 30:59.091
HEY, PAL,
WE'RE TAKING A VIDEO

30:59.125 --> 31:00.159
OF THE WHOLE FAMILY.

31:00.192 --> 31:02.094
CARE TO JOIN US?

31:02.128 --> 31:04.163
- WHAT DO YOU WANT ME FOR?

31:08.200 --> 31:09.168
[door closes]

31:09.201 --> 31:13.639
*

31:13.672 --> 31:18.044
[men moaning]

31:47.473 --> 31:50.376
- A BETTER OFFER
COMES ALONG.

32:03.990 --> 32:07.960
[men moaning, chuckling]

32:07.994 --> 32:10.262
- OH, YEAH.

32:12.731 --> 32:15.434
- THAT'LL BE $5.25.

32:15.467 --> 32:17.603
THANKS.

32:17.636 --> 32:20.439
ANOTHER SATISFIED
CUSTOMER.

32:20.472 --> 32:22.441
- YOU KNOW, YOU SAY THAT
EVERY TIME YOU SELL ONE.

32:22.474 --> 32:24.510
- I DO?
WELL, IT MUST BE TRUE.

32:24.543 --> 32:27.113
WE'VE SOLD 536 COPIES
ON THE WEBSITE

32:27.146 --> 32:28.580
AND ALMOST 200 HERE
IN THE STORE.

32:28.614 --> 32:30.316
- THOSE ARE ALL
WE HAVE LEFT.

32:30.349 --> 32:33.452
- EVERYBODY LOVES THAT
J.T. FINALLY GOT HIS MAN.

32:33.485 --> 32:35.654
- YEAH, EVERYONE
BUT YOU-KNOW-WHO.

32:35.687 --> 32:39.325
- YEAH, I DO KNOW WHO.

32:39.358 --> 32:41.760
WELL, WHAT DID YOU EXPECT?

32:41.793 --> 32:44.230
- WHAT DID I EXPECT?

32:44.263 --> 32:48.234
THAT LIFE MIGHT IMITATE ART?

32:48.267 --> 32:51.203
I'VE HEARD IT'S BEEN KNOWN
TO HAPPEN.

32:51.237 --> 32:53.072
AW, HOW COULD
I HAVE BEEN SUCKERED

32:53.105 --> 32:54.106
INTO MY OWN FANTASY?

32:54.140 --> 32:56.742
TALK ABOUT PATHETIC.

32:56.775 --> 32:58.610
NOBODY ON EARTH KNOWS
BETTER THAN I DO

32:58.644 --> 33:00.146
THAT UNLESS HE WERE
GENETICALLY ALTERED

33:00.179 --> 33:01.513
BY SOME NUCLEAR MISHAP,

33:01.547 --> 33:03.749
THAT COULD NEVER HAPPEN.

33:03.782 --> 33:05.617
- NOT A BAD STORY.

33:05.651 --> 33:08.154
- MM.
BUT THAT'S ALL IT IS.

33:08.187 --> 33:09.488
IT'S A STORY.

33:09.521 --> 33:11.223
[door bells jangle]

33:11.257 --> 33:16.362
- DO YOU HAVE
THE NEW ISSUE OF RAGE?

33:16.395 --> 33:18.397
THIS IS TOTALLY AWESOME.

33:21.400 --> 33:23.602
- ANOTHER SATISFIED CUSTOMER.

33:25.271 --> 33:27.273
- [groans]

33:29.275 --> 33:33.145
WELL, I THINK THE HOUSE
HAS BEEN OFFICIALLY WARMED,

33:33.179 --> 33:36.348
WOULDN'T YOU SAY?

33:37.716 --> 33:39.251
GREAT PARTY, HUH?

33:39.285 --> 33:41.420
EVERYBODY SEEMED
TO HAVE A GOOD TIME.

33:43.689 --> 33:46.125
- YEAH.

33:46.158 --> 33:48.827
IF YOU CALL MELANIE AND LINDSAY
DECLARING A CEASE-FIRE,

33:48.860 --> 33:52.064
BRIAN LEAVING TO GO
TO A SEX PARTY,

33:52.098 --> 33:54.166
AND YOU AND MICHAEL STICKING
THAT FUCKING CAMERA

33:54.200 --> 33:56.268
IN MY FACE PRETENDING
WE'RE THIS HAPPY FAMILY

33:56.302 --> 33:57.403
HAVING A "GOOD TIME."

33:57.436 --> 34:01.173
- WE'RE NOT PRETENDING.
WE ARE.

34:05.511 --> 34:08.414
YOU'RE GOING TO GET
THROUGH THIS.

34:08.447 --> 34:11.217
I PROMISE.

34:11.250 --> 34:14.720
- FUCK YOUR FALSE HOPE.

34:14.753 --> 34:18.190
THE WORLD'S
A STINKING SHITHOLE.

34:20.459 --> 34:23.329
- [sighs]

34:23.362 --> 34:25.597
I DON'T THINK SARTRE
COULD HAVE SAID IT ANY BETTER.

34:25.631 --> 34:28.200
- WHO?

34:29.868 --> 34:33.839
- LISTEN, I-I FOUND
A GREAT CHARTER SCHOOL.

34:33.872 --> 34:35.607
THEY HAVE
A WAITING LIST A MILE LONG,

34:35.641 --> 34:37.376
BUT ONE OF THE PROFESSORS
IN MY DEPARTMENT

34:37.409 --> 34:38.844
IS ON THE BOARD, SO I WAS
ABLE TO PULL A FEW STRINGS--

34:38.877 --> 34:41.580
- WHY EVEN BOTHER, HUH?

34:41.613 --> 34:42.781
THEY'LL JUST FIND
OUT THERE TOO,

34:42.814 --> 34:47.186
AND THEN IT WILL
START ALL OVER AGAIN.

34:47.219 --> 34:51.390
SO WHAT'S THE POINT OF MY GOING
TO ANOTHER FUCKING SCHOOL?

34:59.431 --> 35:01.099
- [sighs]

35:03.769 --> 35:06.738
- I HAVEN'T BEEN HERE
SINCE YOU LEFT.

35:06.772 --> 35:08.874
SOMEHOW IT'S NOT THE SAME.

35:08.907 --> 35:10.476
- YEAH.

35:10.509 --> 35:14.213
NEITHER AM I.

35:14.246 --> 35:16.348
CARL...

35:16.382 --> 35:21.820
HONEY, I FOUND OUT
WHAT'S WRONG WITH ME.

35:21.853 --> 35:24.623
- I JUST WANT YOU
TO KNOW...

35:24.656 --> 35:29.161
THAT WHATEVER IT IS...

35:29.195 --> 35:30.762
I'M IN THIS
FOR THE LONG HAUL.

35:30.796 --> 35:34.666
I'LL STAND BY YOU.
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

35:34.700 --> 35:36.402
- I KNOW THAT,
SWEETHEART.

35:36.435 --> 35:37.669
THAT'S WHY
I LOVE YOU.

35:37.703 --> 35:40.172
- OKAY. TELL ME.

35:40.206 --> 35:44.510
NO, WAIT. WAIT.

35:44.543 --> 35:46.312
OKAY. TELL ME.

35:46.345 --> 35:48.514
- FIRST OF ALL,

35:48.547 --> 35:49.781
IT'S NOT A PHYSICAL THING.

35:49.815 --> 35:51.917
- OH!

35:51.950 --> 35:54.386
OOH.

35:54.420 --> 35:56.522
THAT'S A RELIEF.
- YEAH.

35:56.555 --> 36:00.259
- THEN WHAT?

36:00.292 --> 36:04.530
- IT'S HARD TO EXPLAIN.

36:04.563 --> 36:08.267
EVER SINCE I LEFT HERE,
I'VE FELT LOST.

36:08.300 --> 36:09.668
I HAVE NO PLACE TO GO,

36:09.701 --> 36:11.537
I GOT NOTHING TO DO
BUT SIT AT HOME

36:11.570 --> 36:14.440
AND BUY A LOT OF SHIT
THAT I DON'T WANT OFF THE TV.

36:14.473 --> 36:16.808
- THAT'S WHAT A LADY
OF LEISURE'S SUPPOSED TO DO.

36:16.842 --> 36:19.711
I MEAN, YOU KNOW, RELAX.
ENJOY YOURSELF.

36:19.745 --> 36:22.981
BE GLAD YOU
DON'T HAVE TO WORK.

36:23.014 --> 36:25.417
- IT'S FUNNY, I NEVER THOUGHT
OF IT AS WORK.

36:25.451 --> 36:29.755
- ALL THOSE LONG, HARD HOURS
ON YOUR FEET?

36:29.788 --> 36:30.989
JUGGLING PLATES?

36:31.022 --> 36:34.593
- TO ME, IT WAS MORE
LIKE A DANCE.

36:34.626 --> 36:37.429
AND I WAS
THE PRIMA BALLERINA.

36:37.463 --> 36:38.697
- THIS IS NOT EXACTLY

36:38.730 --> 36:43.502
THE ROYAL BALLET
OF PITTSBURGH.

36:43.535 --> 36:46.372
- BUT IT'S MY JOB.

36:46.405 --> 36:49.007
NO, IT'S MORE THAN A JOB.

36:49.040 --> 36:53.345
IT'S WHO I AM.

36:53.379 --> 36:56.348
AND I WANT IT BACK.

36:56.382 --> 36:58.917
- [sighs]

36:58.950 --> 37:01.487
I-I WAS JUST...

37:01.520 --> 37:03.989
TRYING TO MAKE IT
EASIER ON YOU, HONEY.

37:04.022 --> 37:08.527
BUT IF THIS'LL MAKE
YOU HAPPY...

37:08.560 --> 37:10.362
[laughs]

37:10.396 --> 37:12.030
LIKE I SAID,

37:12.063 --> 37:14.333
I'LL STAND BY YOU.

37:14.366 --> 37:17.603
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

37:17.636 --> 37:21.273
- THANK YOU, CARL.

37:23.375 --> 37:24.910
NOW, YOU'RE SURE
YOU'RE OKAY WITH THIS?

37:24.943 --> 37:26.745
- [scoffs]

37:26.778 --> 37:28.647
100% SURE.

37:28.680 --> 37:30.382
- GOOD...

37:30.416 --> 37:32.818
'CAUSE MY SHIFT STARTED
FIVE MINUTES AGO.

37:32.851 --> 37:35.887
- [laughs]

37:35.921 --> 37:37.623
SO...

37:37.656 --> 37:38.624
WHAT'LL IT BE?

37:38.657 --> 37:41.293
[both laughing]

37:41.327 --> 37:45.431
[both groaning, grunting]

37:51.537 --> 37:54.473
- [chuckling]

37:58.076 --> 38:00.679
WHOO!

38:00.712 --> 38:01.680
THAT WAS HOT!

38:01.713 --> 38:04.082
[groans]

38:04.115 --> 38:05.517
- THINK SO?

38:05.551 --> 38:07.719
- [panting]
YEAH...

38:09.955 --> 38:13.392
YOU KNOW,
I'VE BEEN HERE BEFORE.

38:13.425 --> 38:15.594
- OH?

38:15.627 --> 38:17.095
- I MEAN
IN THIS BUILDING.

38:17.128 --> 38:20.732
FUCKED SOME POOR LOSER.

38:20.766 --> 38:22.601
- YEAH, WELL...

38:22.634 --> 38:24.436
THE PLACE IS CRAWLING
WITH THEM.

38:24.470 --> 38:25.671
BELIEVE ME, I KNOW.

38:25.704 --> 38:27.806
- [laughs]

38:27.839 --> 38:30.942
ONE OF MY PITY FUCKS.

38:30.976 --> 38:32.411
- YEAH, SPEAKING
OF PITY FUCKS--

38:32.444 --> 38:33.845
- YOU KNOW,

38:33.879 --> 38:36.415
WHEN WE FIRST HOOKED UP
AT THE GYM,

38:36.448 --> 38:37.416
I WASN'T SURE.

38:37.449 --> 38:38.950
- THAT I WAS YOUR TYPE?

38:38.984 --> 38:42.721
- THAT YOU'D BE SO HOT.

38:42.754 --> 38:46.124
BUT, MAN, ARE YOU EVER.

38:46.157 --> 38:47.959
LOOK.

38:47.993 --> 38:51.763
I'M STILL HARD.

38:51.797 --> 38:55.701
YOU UP FOR ANOTHER ROUND?

38:55.734 --> 38:57.903
- ACTUALLY THERE'S SOMETHING
I WANT TO SAY TO YOU.

38:57.936 --> 39:00.939
- THAT YOU WANT TO ROLL ME
OVER AND FUCK ME AGAIN?

39:05.076 --> 39:08.880
- WHAT I WANT TO--

39:08.914 --> 39:12.150
WHAT I WANT TO SAY TO--
TO YOU...

39:12.183 --> 39:16.722
IS, UH...

39:16.755 --> 39:19.090
ROLL OVER.

39:22.160 --> 39:23.895
- OH, YEAH.

39:25.564 --> 39:27.766
- MICHAEL, WE CAN'T FORCE HIM
TO GO TO SCHOOL.

39:27.799 --> 39:29.468
- OF COURSE WE CAN.
WE'RE HIS PARENTS.

39:29.501 --> 39:30.802
HELL, HE'S ONLY 17.

39:30.836 --> 39:32.471
- YOU CAN QUIT SCHOOL
WHEN YOU'RE 16.

39:32.504 --> 39:34.139
BESIDES, IF WE PRESSURE HIM,

39:34.172 --> 39:35.907
WE'LL ONLY PUSH HIM AWAY MORE.

39:35.941 --> 39:37.609
- HE'S GOT TO FINISH
HIGH SCHOOL,

39:37.643 --> 39:38.777
SO HE CAN GO TO COLLEGE

39:38.810 --> 39:40.512
AND BECOME
A DOCTOR AND A LAWYER

39:40.546 --> 39:42.814
AND PRESIDENT OF
THE UNITED STATES.

39:45.817 --> 39:47.486
WHAT WAS THAT FOR?
- THE ETERNAL OPTIMIST.

39:47.519 --> 39:49.020
THAT'S WHY I LOVE YOU.

39:49.054 --> 39:51.523
NOW, LET'S JUST GIVE HIM
SOME TIME AND SOME SPACE,

39:51.557 --> 39:54.660
AND HOPEFULLY HE'LL COME
TO THE RIGHT DECISION.

40:01.533 --> 40:05.571
- OH. HEY, I WAS JUST ABOUT
TO CALL YOU FOR DINNER.

40:05.604 --> 40:07.072
JUST BECAUSE I SAID
WE'RE HAVING SLOPPY JOES

40:07.105 --> 40:08.774
DOESN'T MEAN WE'RE GOING
TO GO CAMPING.

40:08.807 --> 40:09.908
- GOING SOMEWHERE?

40:09.941 --> 40:11.777
- YEAH.

40:11.810 --> 40:12.844
- WELL, EAT FIRST

40:12.878 --> 40:14.680
AND DON'T BE OUT TOO LATE.

40:14.713 --> 40:18.517
- I MEAN I'M LEAVING.

40:18.550 --> 40:20.018
FOR GOOD.

40:23.489 --> 40:24.790
- WH--WHAT DO YOU
MEAN YOU'RE--

40:24.823 --> 40:27.225
- I CAN'T STAY HERE
ANYMORE, OKAY?

40:27.258 --> 40:29.194
- NO, IT'S NOT OKAY.

40:29.227 --> 40:32.564
NOW PUT YOUR THINGS AWAY
AND SIT DOWN AND EAT,

40:32.598 --> 40:34.533
AND AFTERWARDS
WE'LL DISCUSS THIS.

40:34.566 --> 40:37.068
- WE'VE ALREADY DISCUSSED IT.
THERE'S NOTHING LEFT TO SAY.

40:37.102 --> 40:38.670
- WELL, I SAID YOU'RE
NOT GOING ANYWHERE,

40:38.704 --> 40:39.938
AND THAT'S FINAL!
- HEY, MICHAEL, MICHAEL.

40:39.971 --> 40:41.607
- WHAT?
HE CAN'T JUST LEAVE!

40:41.640 --> 40:43.475
WE'RE HIS PARENTS,
FOR CHRIST'S SAKES,

40:43.509 --> 40:45.577
WHETHER HE LIKES IT OR NOT.
WE'RE HIS LEGAL GUARDIANS.

40:45.611 --> 40:46.945
WHAT WE SAY GOES.
- HUNTER, HUNTER,

40:46.978 --> 40:48.847
NOTHING IS GOING TO BE SOLVED
BY RUNNING AWAY.

40:48.880 --> 40:51.149
- I DON'T BELONG HERE!
I DON'T BELONG IN THIS HOUSE,

40:51.182 --> 40:53.619
I DON'T BELONG AT THAT SCHOOL.
AND I DON'T BELONG WITH YOU!

40:53.652 --> 40:55.554
- OF COURSE YOU BELONG
WITH US.

40:55.587 --> 40:58.089
- I'LL ONLY GO ON
CAUSING YOU PROBLEMS,

40:58.123 --> 40:59.491
EMBARRASSING YOU.

40:59.525 --> 41:00.959
- YOU DON'T EMBARRASS US.

41:00.992 --> 41:02.027
WE'RE PROUD OF YOU.

41:02.060 --> 41:03.562
- THIS I-IS NOT
THE DEBATE TEAM.

41:03.595 --> 41:05.030
THERE'S NO ARGUMENT HERE,

41:05.063 --> 41:09.134
EXCEPT DO YOU WANT APPLESAUCE
OR CANNED PEACHES?

41:09.167 --> 41:11.036
HUNTER!

41:11.069 --> 41:14.139
I DON'T CARE IF I HAVE TO LOCK
YOU IN YOUR FUCKING ROOM.

41:19.611 --> 41:21.146
- WHERE'RE YOU GOING TO GO?
- I DON'T KNOW.

41:21.179 --> 41:22.714
- DO YOU HAVE ANY MONEY?

41:22.748 --> 41:24.583
- WHAT YOU AND MICHAEL GAVE ME
FOR MY BIRTHDAY.

41:24.616 --> 41:26.017
- NO PLAN, NO MONEY.
PERFECT.

41:26.051 --> 41:27.653
HOW DO YOU INTEND
TO SUPPORT YOURSELF?

41:27.686 --> 41:28.720
- I'LL THINK OF SOMETHING.

41:28.754 --> 41:31.857
- I BET YOU WILL.

41:31.890 --> 41:34.726
- HEY. HEY.

41:34.760 --> 41:38.664
IF YOU NEED MORE, CALL US.

41:38.697 --> 41:40.799
- WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING?

41:49.174 --> 41:51.076
HUNTER, WAIT.

41:55.781 --> 41:58.717
JUST PUT IT IN YOUR SHOE,
SOMEPLACE SAFE.

42:08.827 --> 42:09.928
[door closes]

42:15.601 --> 42:17.302
- HOT OR NOT?

42:17.335 --> 42:18.937
- IT'S HOT.

42:22.340 --> 42:25.543
- NOW, THAT'S WHAT I CALL
A RESOUNDING APPROVAL.

42:28.680 --> 42:30.181
- BY THE WAY, WE SOLD
OUT EVERY LAST COPY

42:30.215 --> 42:32.317
OF THE MARRIAGE ISSUE,

42:32.350 --> 42:36.722
AND WE GOT ORDERS
FOR OVER 300 MORE.

42:36.755 --> 42:38.256
- IF NOT HAVING ANY BALLS

42:38.289 --> 42:42.794
